    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I'm also hearing a lot of noise about how these raises are 'necessary' for the workers in our community to keep up with inflation. From a business consultancy perspective, is there any actual data showing that these higher wages help the local economy in the long run, or is it mostly just a moral argument?",
