    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That \"positive feedback loop\" sounds good in theory, but for a small owner like me, it feels like a massive gamble. If my costs go up now, I might not even survive long enough to see that \"robust economy\" happen. Isn't it a bit risky to assume that higher wages won't just lead to layoffs or businesses closing down instead of more spending?",
